        {
          "name": "Stream (SSE)",
          "description": "Respostas em tempo real via **Server-Sent Events** (`text/event-stream`).\n\nEnvie `\"stream\": true` no body. Eventos:\n- `meta` — modelo, categoria, cache_hit, tipo_usuario\n- `token` — `{\"content\": \"...\"}` (texto chegando)\n- `done` — resposta completa + `sessao_id`\n\nNo Postman, use **Send** e veja a resposta bruta na aba Body; o script Tests acumula o texto em `{{stream_text}}`.",
          "item": [
            {
              "name": "Chat stream — olá",
              "event": [
                {
                  "listen": "test",
                  "script": {
                    "exec": [
                      "function parseSseProfinho(text) {",
                      "    let accumulated = \"\";",
                      "    let donePayload = null;",
                      "    for (const block of text.split(/\\n\\n+/)) {",
                      "        if (!block.trim()) continue;",
                      "        const eventMatch = block.match(/^event:\\s*(\\w+)/m);",
                      "        const dataMatch = block.match(/^data:\\s*(.+)$/m);",
                      "        if (!eventMatch || !dataMatch) continue;",
                      "        try {",
                      "            const payload = JSON.parse(dataMatch[1]);",
                      "            if (eventMatch[1] === \"token\" && payload.content) accumulated += payload.content;",
                      "            if (eventMatch[1] === \"done\") donePayload = payload;",
                      "        } catch (e) {}",
                      "    }",
                      "    return { accumulated, donePayload };",
                      "}",
                      "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                      "    const { accumulated, donePayload } = parseSseProfinho(pm.response.text());",
                      "    pm.collectionVariables.set(\"stream_text\", accumulated);",
                      "    if (donePayload && donePayload.sessao_id) pm.collectionVariables.set(\"sessao_id\", donePayload.sessao_id);",
                      "    pm.test(\"SSE content-type\", () => pm.expect(pm.response.headers.get(\"Content-Type\")).to.include(\"text/event-stream\"));",
                      "    pm.test(\"Tokens recebidos\", () => pm.expect(accumulated.length).to.be.above(0));",
                      "    pm.test(\"Evento done\", () => pm.expect(donePayload).to.not.be.null);",
                      "    console.log(\"Resposta stream:\", accumulated);",
                      "}"
                    ],
                    "type": "text/javascript"
                  }
                }
              ],
              "request": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [
                  { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
                  { "key": "Accept", "value": "text/event-stream" }
                ],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\n  \"prompt\": \"olá\",\n  \"stream\": true,\n  \"categoria\": \"chat\",\n  \"temperature\": 0.7,\n  \"usar_web\": false,\n  \"salvar\": true\n}"
                },
                "url": "{{baseUrl}}/chat",
                "description": "Saudação com streaming token a token (modelo light)."
              }
            },
